            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Hd1e108">Rubrica 9</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De gratia et gratitudine et ingratitudine</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e114">
              De gratia et grati<lb ed="#K" n="24" break="no"/>tudine et ingratitudine. Rubrica. 9
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e121">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e117">Psalmista 36 pslamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e125">Mutuabitur 
              <lb ed="#K"/>peccator et non soluet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e133">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e131">Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 17.</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e137">Qui redit 
              <lb ed="#K"/>mala pro bonis non recedet 
              <lb ed="#K"/>malum de domo eius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e146">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e145">Aristoteles rethoricorum lib. 2. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e150">Factiua amicitie est 
              <lb ed="#K"/>gratia: et non requisitum facere:
              <lb ed="#K"/>et cum fecerint non manifestare.
              <lb ed="#K"/>Sic enim ipsi gratia videtur: non propter a<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>lterum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e160">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e159">Idem ethicorum libro 5. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e162">Re<lb ed="#K" n="1" break="no"/>tributio 
                  <pb ed="#K" n="85-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#K" n="a"/>
               est proprium gratiae: refa<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>mulari 
               enim oportet ei qui gratiam fecit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e174">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e178">Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 28 
              <lb ed="#K"/>scilicet de aristotele:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e178">Aristoteles quesitus quid 
              <lb ed="#K"/>citius senescat: inquit gratia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e186">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e193">Iesus filius sirach in ecc. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e190">Non fit 
              <lb ed="#K"/>porrecta manus tua ad 
              <lb ed="#K"/>accipiendum: et ad dandum collecta.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e198">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e205">29. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e200">Multi quasi inuentionem
              <lb ed="#K"/>estimauerunt fenus: et pres<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>titerunt 
              molestiam his qui se 
              <lb ed="#K"/>adiuuauerunt: donec accipiant
              <lb ed="#K"/>osculantur manus dantis: et in 
              <lb ed="#K"/>promissionibus humiliant vocem 
              <lb ed="#K"/>suam: et in tempore: redditionis postu<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>labat 
              tempus: et loquitur verba tedii 
              <lb ed="#K"/>et murmurationem: et tempus causabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e217">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e228">29. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e219">Gratiam fideiussoris ne 
               <lb ed="#K"/>obliuiscaris: dedit enim pro te 
               <lb ed="#K"/>animam suam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e228">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e243">Terentius in andria. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e232">Si illum obiurges vite 
              <lb ed="#K"/>qui auxilium tulit: Quid faci<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>as 
              illi: qui dederit damnum aut 
              <lb ed="#K"/>malum:</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e240">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e257">Tullius retho. artis vereris li. i. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e244">His qui ne bre<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>cessario 
              non profuerunt haberi gratiam 
              <lb ed="#K"/>non oportet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e252">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e269">Li. 2 c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e254">Gratia est 
              <lb ed="#K"/>virtus in qua amicitiarum et of<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ficiorum 
              alterius memoria et 
              <lb ed="#K"/>remunerandi voluntas continetur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e262">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e281">Idem philipicorum libro 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e264">Cui gratia 
              <lb ed="#K"/>referri tanta non potest quan<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ta 
              debetur: habenda tamen tanta 
              <lb ed="#K"/>est quantam maximam animi nostri ca<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>pere 
              possunt</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e274">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e298">Ouidius sine titulo seu amorum libro i. c. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e278">Gratia 
                  <cb ed="#K" n="b"/>
              <lb ed="#K"/>pro rebus merito debetur ineptis
              <lb ed="#K"/>Omnia conductor soluit: mercede 
              <lb ed="#K"/>soluta Non manet officio: debitor 
              <lb ed="#K"/>ille suo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e288">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e313">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 13 e. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e292">Ingratus
              <lb ed="#K"/>est qui beneficium reddit 
              <lb ed="#K"/>sine vsura. Ingratus est 
              <lb ed="#K"/>qui reddit. Ingratissimus omnium qui 
              <lb ed="#K"/>oblitus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e307">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e331">Idem de moribus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e309">Me<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>moria 
               beneficiorum fragilis est: 
               <lb ed="#K"/>iniuriarum tenax.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e317">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e346">Marcialis cocus epigramaton. libro. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e321">Non 
              <lb ed="#K"/>reddet sterilis: semina iacta 
              <lb ed="#K"/>seges.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e327">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e357">Ualerius max. li. 5. ti. de gratis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e331">Gaii marii non 
              <lb ed="#K"/>solum precipuus: sed etiam praepotens 
              <lb ed="#K"/>grate mentis fuit impetus. 
              <lb ed="#K"/>Duas enim camentium cohortes 
              <lb ed="#K"/>mira virtute vim cimbrorum sustinen<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tes 
              in ipsa acie aduersus conditi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>onem 
              fedeis ciuitate donauit
              <lb ed="#K"/>Quod quidem factum et vere et e<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>gregie 
              excusauit: dicendo: in<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ter 
              armorum strepitum verba se 
              <lb ed="#K"/>iuris ciuilis exaudire non 
              <lb ed="#K"/>potuisse: et sane id tempus tunc 
              <lb ed="#K"/>erat quo magis defendere quam 
              <lb ed="#K"/>audire leges oportebat. Mi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tridates 
              rex magnifice gratus 
              <lb ed="#K"/>apparuit: qui pro leonico acerrimo 
              <lb ed="#K"/>salutis sue defensore a rho<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>diis 
              nauali pugna excepto 
              <lb ed="#K"/>omnes hostium captiuos permutauit.
              <lb ed="#K"/>Satis esse existimans ab inui<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ctissimis 
              circumueniri quam ben<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>merito 
              gratiam non referre:</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e341">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e404">Ti.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#K"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e343">de ingratis dandi et accipiendi 
                  <pb ed="#K" n="85-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#K" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#K" n="1"/>beneficii commercium: sine quo vita ho<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>minum 
               est mors tollit quisque 
               <lb ed="#K"/>benemerito parem referre gratiam 
               <lb ed="#K"/>negligit. Ligurgo neque vite 
               <lb ed="#K"/>summe synceritas neque constan<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tissimus 
               erga patriam amor 
               <lb ed="#K"/>neque leges salutariter excogi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tate 
               Sepe enim lapidibus pe<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>titus 
               publico furore priuatus etiam 
               <lb ed="#K"/>oculo ad vltimum ipsa patria lace<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>demonum 
               pulsus est. Quid alie 
               <lb ed="#K"/>facient vrbes vbi etiam illa 
               <lb ed="#K"/>que constantie et grauita<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>tis 
               eximiam sibi laudem vendi<lb ed="#K"/>cauit 
               tam ingrata aduersus tam 
               <lb ed="#K"/>benemeritum extitit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e402">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e442">Ambrosius de officiis li. i. c. 30.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e406">Non dare 
              <lb ed="#K"/>cuiquam non reddere vero non licet. 
              <lb ed="#K"/>Conferre gratiam bonum est: 
              <lb ed="#K"/>at qui referire nescit durissimus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e416">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e458">Cato. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e420">memor accepti 
              <lb ed="#K"/>beneficii esto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e424">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e469">Cap. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e428">Officium alterius 
              <lb ed="#K"/>multi narrare memento Atque 
              <lb ed="#K"/>aliis cum tu benefeceris ipse fi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>leto
              Exiguum munus: cum dat 
              <lb ed="#K"/>tibi pauper amicus Accipito 
              <lb ed="#K"/>placide: et plene laudare memento.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e439">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e489">Uersificator fabularum esopi.
              <lb ed="#K"/>fab 8</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e443">Nil prodest prodesse ma<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>lis: 
              mens praua molorum Im<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>memor 
              accepti non timet esse 
              <lb ed="#K"/>boni.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e451">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e502">Fabula. 10</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e453">Reddere gaudet 
              <lb ed="#K"/>homo nequa pro melle venenum. 
              <lb ed="#K"/>Pro fructum penam: pro pietate dolum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e463"> 
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e514">Fabula. 42</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e465">Non debet meritum 
              <lb ed="#K"/>turpis delere vetustas Accepti 
              <lb ed="#K"/>memores: nos decet esse boni.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e467">
                  <cb ed="#K" n="b"/>
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e527">Andreas ad gualterium de 
              <lb ed="#K"/>amore lib. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e471">Maioribus censetur 
              <lb ed="#K"/>meritis dignus qui bona spon<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>te 
              peregit: quam qui ea coactus 
              <lb ed="#K"/>exercuit. Coacta nemini sunt 
              <lb ed="#K"/>grata obsequia: et nullis 
              <lb ed="#K"/>digna premiis iudicantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e488">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e548">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 23</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e492">Accepti 
              <lb ed="#K"/>semper muneris esto memor A quocum<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>que 
              tibi praesertim paupere factum Com<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>pensare 
              stude: merito seruitium.
              <lb ed="#K"/>Frigescit dantis animus cum vi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>derit 
              ipse Cui dederit ingratum: 
              <lb ed="#K"/>muneris esse sibi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e506">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e566">c. 25</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e508">Noli 
              <lb ed="#K"/>serpentem dico tibi fili nutrire Mor<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>debit 
              quoniam te prius ipse malus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e516">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e579">Mattheus vindocinensis de hi<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>stor. 
              tobie c 31.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e520">Non tibi quod da<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>bitur: 
              sed cur intellige: quia Sola 
              <lb ed="#K"/>voluntatis forma inonerat 
              <lb ed="#K"/>opus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e529">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e594">Auctor li. de moribus medicorum. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e533">Ingratos homines 
              <lb ed="#K"/>inflata superbia reddit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e541">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e607">Bellinus in speculo vite parte. i. exem. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e545">Seruit<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>ium 
              nullus perdit: quod reddere 
              <lb ed="#K"/>multi Desistunt: reddit vnicus 
              <lb ed="#K"/>illud homo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-d1e553">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Rd1e620">Prouerb. vulgar:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38489-Qd1e557">A caual dona: non guardar endente.
              <lb ed="#K"/>Chi laua el cauo ala<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>seno <!--double check-->
              perde el sauone Chi serue ad
              <lb ed="#K"/>ario segnore ne grao ne guerdone <!--this is different edit later-->
              <lb ed="#K"/>Chi despicha el laro apicha si.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
